大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 标志性专辑封面背后的艺术家为“创新”战争儿童展览创作新作品https://www.nme.com/uncategorised/artist-behind-iconic-david-bowie-album-covers-creates-new-work-for-innovative-war-child-exhibition-3781988?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=标志性大卫·鲍伊专辑封面背后的艺术家为创新战争儿童展览创作新作品Laura MolloyThu, 08 Aug 2024 10:09:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsUncategorisedRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3781988 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·鲍伊和乔治·安德伍德。图片来源：乔治·安德伍德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此次筹款展览和拍卖会汇聚了 30 名艺术家，他们的创作灵感源自这位歌手 1974 年的热门单曲《Rebel Rebel》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/uncategorised/artist-behind-iconic-david-bowie-album-covers-creates-new-work-for-innovative-war-child-exhibition-3781988">大卫·鲍伊标志性专辑封面背后的后艺术家为“创新”战争儿童展览创作了新作品，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·鲍伊和乔治·安德伍德。图片来源：乔治·安德伍德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/David-Bowie-and-George-Underwood.-Credit_-George-Underwood-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>大卫·鲍伊 (David <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">Bowie</a> ) 一些最具标志性的专辑封面背后的艺术家乔治·安德伍德 (George Underwood) 向即将举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/war-child">战争儿童</a>慈善展览捐赠了一幅新画。请在下面找到更多详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/david-bowie-a-portrait-of-the-artist-as-a-young-man-as-told-by-those-who-knew-him-best-2443649"><b>大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 的早年经历——最了解他的人讲述的</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>War Child 是一家为 15 个国家冲突地区的儿童及其家庭提供支持的慈善机构，本周早些时候宣布推出“声音与视觉”——“创新筹款展览和全球在线拍卖”。由 Art On A Postcard 策划的年度展览将看到艺术家对一首标志性歌词做出回应，以提高人们对受冲突影响的儿童的认识并为其提供资金。</p><p>在其成立之年，安德伍德是 33 位当代顶尖艺术家之一，他们的作品灵感源自鲍伊的歌词“我们喜欢跳舞，我们看起来很神圣”，这句歌词取自已故歌手 1974 年的热门单曲《Rebel Rebel》。</p><p>该展览将于 9 月 26 日至 27 日在伦敦 180 Studios 举行，全球在线拍卖将于 9 月 17 日至 10 月 1 日举行。您可以<a href="https://artonapostcard.com/pages/sound-and-vision" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处将其添加到您的日历中</a>。</p><p>在学校相遇后，安德伍德和鲍伊组建了一支乐队。然而，在安德伍德为一个女孩打架时殴打鲍伊后，他们的音乐合作关系并没有持续下去。然而，几年后，安德伍德为鲍伊最伟大的专辑《Hunky Dory》和《Ziggy Stardust》以及第一张<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/t-rex">霸王龙</a>专辑封面创作了艺术作品。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.