内莉因持有摇头丸且没有保险证明而被捕https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-arrested-for-possession-of-ecstasy-and-no-proof-of-insurance-3781960?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nelly-arrested-for-拥有摇头丸且无保险证明Laura MolloyThu, 08 Aug 2024 09:20:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3781960 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="耐莉.图片来源：史蒂夫·詹宁斯/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱歌手周三凌晨在密苏里州被捕，现已被释放</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-arrested-for-possession-of-ecstasy-and-no-proof-of-insurance-3781960">内莉因持有摇头丸而被捕且没有保险证明的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="耐莉.图片来源：史蒂夫·詹宁斯/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nelly.-Credit_-Steve-Jennings_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，内莉因持有摇头丸且没有保险而被捕。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/celebrity/rapper-nelly-arrested-st-louis-area-charges-possessing-ecstasy-not-ins-rcna165627" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NBC新闻报道</em></a>，内莉（Nelly），真名康奈尔·海恩斯二世（Cornell Haynes II），于周三（8月7日）凌晨4点45分在美国密苏里州圣路易斯郊区马里兰高地被捕。</p><p>这位说唱歌手被州巡逻队带到马里兰高地警察局，在那里他因郊区交通指控而未能出庭而被捕。他还被指控持有四颗摇头丸（一种管制药物），并且没有保险。</p><p>根据州巡逻记录，内莉现已被释放。</p><p>内莉的律师斯科特·罗森布鲁姆在一份声明中回应了这些指控，否认了持有毒品的指控。罗森布鲁姆说：“[内利]自 2018 年起因‘无保险证明’而被捕，逮捕令于 2023 年 12 月发出，但他没有收到任何通知。” </p><figure id="attachment_3383384" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3383384" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3383384" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Nelly-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3383384" class="wp-caption-text">耐莉.图片来源：Joe Scarnici/LIV Golf via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>声明称，内利是“一名过分热心、不合规矩的警官的目标”，内利在一家赌场赢了一定金额后，该警官对他进行了背景调查，并在那里被捕。根据罗森布鲁姆的说法，内利此前在同一场地赢得“类似或更多金额”时无需接受背景调查。</p><p>他说，这名警官给内莉戴上手铐，“并带他穿过赌场”，然后“在没有合理理由的情况下进行了搜查，他声称在内莉的个人物品中发现了所谓的‘摇头丸’”。</p><p>罗森布鲁姆说，内莉“经常被要求提供没有搜查令的证据。包括联邦调查局检查”，作为国际旅行的要求。他接着说：“没有。”</p><p> “我百分百相信这个案子不会有结果，”罗森布鲁姆继续说道。 “我们将要求对这名警官的行为进行调查。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，耐莉刚刚结束了对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janet-jackson">珍妮·杰克逊</a>“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janet-jackson-announces-together-again-tour-2024-nelly-3572086">再次在一起”巡演</a>的支持。</p><p>内<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nelly-arrested-for-possession-of-ecstasy-and-no-proof-of-insurance-3781960">莉因持有摇头丸而被捕且没有保险证明的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
